[Zinnia-IOP] As an application manager, I want to learn how to change IoP notification settings
fields.System.Description:
5Fresh Ticket
https://needhelp.freshservice.com/a/tickets/7946?current_tab=details

Questions:
  • what kind of alerts, do Zinnia users receive now about incidents?
  • how/from where, can you set an user to receive notifications/alerts?
fields.Custom.Comment:
Associated ticket = [#7946] Fw: Zinnia notification access | needhelp

** Explanation
@Yazan
  • We've created a new email template with code 'iop_defacnoty' and description (Default Approval notifiction on a new approved incident for a Viewer), in Zinnia Menu > Settings > Email templates.
  • We've created a new security role 'IOP Viewer With Approve Notification' (Id/Unique Identifier = iopviewerwithnotification), in Zinnia Menu > Settings > Security Roles
  • Now you can assign users per country for this new security role (click on a security role row from the table, to view the security role's details page and here go to the Members tab)
Now the notification email will be sent to the members of this group, associated with the incident country, when a new incident is approved.
